# Put your Weibo cookie string on ONE line below, then save as:
#   secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
#
# How to get cookie:
# 1. Chrome open https://weibo.com and login
# 2. F12 -> Network -> weibo.cn / weibo.com -> Request Headers -> Cookie
# 3. Paste the Cookie value into secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
#
# crawl4weibo can also auto-fetch visitor cookies via Playwright when this
# file is missing, but logged-in Cookie usually gives better keyword search.
#
# NEVER commit secrets/weibo_cookie.txt
